label: vm ( Forth Inner Interpreter )
  ip w MOV
  ip INC
  t w iLOAD
  t w MOV
  primitive t SUB
  t -if w iJMP then ( jump straight to VM functions )
  ++rp
  ip {rp} iSTORE
  w ip MOV vm a-optim
  vm JMP
